All Implemented Interfaces:
IDialogPage, IMessageProvider, IWizardPage, Listener
public class SNLFilePage
extends WizardNewFileCreationPage

This class takes care of the initialization and creation of the user's desired C file. It determines whether a source (*.st) or header (*.sth) file should be created, and initializes it with a basic main() function.
